Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
Kai-Fu Lee, wani mai saka jari kuma masanin ilimin kere kere wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, ya ce yayin da China ke kara shiga cikin ilimin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a fannin.
An bayyana wannan bayan da bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwa game da AI, kodayake Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da wata dabara ta hukuma don AI.
A halin yanzu, shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta: tana da burin kaiwa matsayi na 1 a cikin abubuwan kirkirar kere kere na AI nan da shekarar 2030.
Lee ya ce, "Rarraba kudaden bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, kuma idan aka yi la'akari da cewa duk sauran ƙasashe suna baya da Amurka, muna tsammanin ci gaba mai girma a fagen AI".
A cikin wata hira da CNN a makon da ya gabata, Lee ya ce ninka kudade zai ninka damar samun babbar nasara ta gaba a fannin kere kere a Amurka.
Lee, wanda littafinsa "All Superpowers: China, Sylson Valley and the New World Order" wanda Hutton Mifflin Harcourt ya buga a wannan watan, shine Shugaba na kamfanin SunVision Venture kuma ya saka hannun jari a cikin ɗayan shahararrun kamfanonin kere kere na kasar Sin Face ++.
Ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a cikin shekarun 1980 akan tsarin kere kere na AI wanda ya doke Attilio, dan wasan Amurka mafi girma, kuma daga baya ya zama Shugaba na Microsoft Research da Shugaban Kamfanin Google a China, Karnemud.
Lee ya yaba wa tsohon gwamnatin Amurka kan gasa ta fasaha kamar ta Robotic Challenge na Hukumar Ci Gaban Binciken Tsaro, kuma ya nemi a gudanar da sabon zagaye don taimakawa wajen gano abubuwan da ke gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amurka galibi suna da wahalar neman tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ba ce ke sabawa shugabannin kimiyya, wadannan cibiyoyi ne", in ji Li.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun dauki manyan masana daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen da aka yi a manufofin shige da fice na taimaka wa Amurka wajen karfafa kokarin da ake yi kan ilimin kere kere.
Ya ce, "Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da Green Card ta atomatik ga masu samun digirin digirgir a fannin kere kere".
A watan Yulin 2017, Majalisar Gwamnatin Sin ta wallafa shirin bunkasa AI na gaba.
Li ya ce Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta kasar Sin, kamar National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati da ke ba da kudade ga masu binciken Amurka, suna tallafawa membobin cibiyoyin ilimi, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya yi kasa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa wani Cibiyar Haɗin gwiwar Artificial Intelligence, wanda ke da niyyar tattara abokan tarayya daga masana'antu da cibiyoyin kimiyya, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin zaɓi kan AI.
Kuma a wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da saka hannun jari na dala miliyan 2 a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
A halin yanzu, NSF tana kashe sama da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara a kan binciken AI.
A lokaci guda, majalisar dokokin Amurka, wacce ke neman kafa kwamitin tsaro na kasa kan batun kere kere, ta yi watanni ba ta dauki mataki ba.
'Yan Macedonia sun kada kuri'ar sauya sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadi ne mutanen Macedonia suka kada kuri'ar sake sunan kasar zuwa "Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia", matakin da zai kawo karshen shekaru da dama da ake fama da rikici da Girka wanda ya hana kokarin shiga kungiyar Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wacce ke da lardin da ake kira Macedonia, tana ganin sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana nufin da'awar yankin nata kuma ta hana ta zama memba a NATO da Tarayyar Turai.
A watan Yuni, gwamnatocin biyu sun cimma yarjejeniya kan sabon sunan da aka gabatar, amma masu adawa da kishin kasa sun yi ikirarin cewa wannan canjin zai cutar da asalin asalin yawancin mutanen Slavic na Macedonia.
Shugaban kasar George Ivanov ya bayyana cewa ba zai kada kuri'a a zaben raba gardama ba, kuma yakin neman zabe ya haifar da hasashe kan ko yawan masu halarta zai cika ka'idar akalla kashi 50 cikin dari na cancantar zaben.
Tambayar da aka yi a kuri'ar ita ce: "Shin kuna son zama memba na NATO da Turai tare da yarjejeniya da Girka?"
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaiavu, sun yi jayayya cewa kokarin da Macedonia ta yi na shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO ya cancanci biyan kudin, wanda ya samo asali daga rushewar Yugoslavia.
"Na zo ne a yau don in yi zabe a madadin makomar kasar nan da kuma matasan Macedonia domin su iya rayuwa da kansu a karkashin inuwar Tarayyar Turai saboda hakan na nufin rayuwa mai aminci ga dukkanmu", in ji Olivera Georgiuska, 'yar shekara 79, a Skopje.
Kodayake ba ta da tilastawa, wasu mambobin majalisar sun ce za su amince da sakamakon zaben don tabbatar da hakan.
Canjin sunan yana buƙatar kuri'ar mafi rinjaye na kashi biyu bisa uku a cikin majalisa.
Hukumar zaben jihar ta ce babu wani rahoto na rashin daidaito har zuwa 1 ga watan Janairu.
Koyaya, yawan masu jefa kuri'a a wannan zaɓe ya kasance kashi 16 cikin ɗari kawai, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34 cikin ɗari a zaɓen majalisar dokoki na 2016 na ƙarshe, inda kashi 66 cikin ɗari na masu jefa ƙuri'a suka yi zabe.
Jos Taniewski, mai shekara 62, mai kada kuri'a a Skopje, babban birnin kasar, ya ce: "Na zo ne don in kada kuri'a ga 'ya'yana, inda muke a Turai".
A ranar 30 ga watan Satumba, 2018, a Stromika, Macedonia, Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaiev, da matarsa Zorica da ɗanta Dusko sun kada kuri'arsu a zaben raba gardama na Macedonia kan sauya sunan ƙasar da zai buɗe hanya zuwa zama memba na NATO da Tarayyar Turai.
A gaban majalisar dokokin Skopje, Vladimir Kavardaco, mai shekaru 54, ya shirya karamin mataki kuma ya kafa wuraren zama a gaban alfarwa da masu hana zaben suka kafa.
Kawardacu ya ce, "Muna goyon bayan kungiyar NATO da EU, amma muna son shiga ne da kai, ba ta hanyar kofa ba".
"Mu talakawa ne, amma muna da daraja.
Idan ba su yarda da mu a matsayin Macedonia ba, za mu iya zuwa wasu wurare kamar China da Rasha kuma mu zama wani ɓangare na haɗin gwiwar Euro-Asia. "
Firayim Minista Zayyo ya ce kasancewa memba a NATO zai jawo hankalin masu zuba jari da ake bukata yayin da rashin aikin yi ya kai kashi 20 cikin dari.
Zayyo ya ce bayan jefa kuri'arsa, "Ina da tabbacin cewa mafiya rinjaye za su goyi bayan hakan saboda sama da kashi 80 cikin 100 na 'yan kasarmu na goyon bayan Tarayyar Turai da NATO".
Ya ce sakamakon "Ee" zai "gyara makomarmu".
Wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Manufofin Macedonia ta fitar a ranar Litinin ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 30 zuwa 43 cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a da ke ƙasa da adadin da ake buƙata don shiga za su shiga cikin kuri'ar.
Wani binciken da talabijin na Macedonia, Telema ya gudanar ya nuna cewa kashi 57 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yanke shawarar kada kuri'a a ranar Lahadi.
Daga cikin wadannan, kashi 70 cikin dari sun ce za su yi zabe a'a.
Don cin nasarar kuri'ar raba gardama, dole ne a samu kashi 50 da kashi daya cikin dari na kuri'un da aka kada.
