Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai kaddamar da taron neman zaben a Willingham, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Trump yana son samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yamma a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a West Virginia a ranar Asabar da karfe 7 na dare agogon Gabas, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon watsa shirye-shiryen taron na Trump na West Virginia a kan layi akan YouTube.
Trump zai yi jawabi a zaman sauraron da dan takarar kotun koli Burt Kavanagh zai yi a wannan makon, wanda ya zama mai matukar tashin hankali saboda zargin cin zarafin mata da ake yi a majalisar dattawa saboda binciken da FBI ta yi na tsawon mako guda.
Amma babban manufar wannan taro mai cike da sha'awa shine taimakawa 'yan Republican, wadanda ke sha'awar gaggauta zaben na Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, ofishin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce taron na mako biyar da ke tafe zai "karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai".
Mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters cewa, "Sarrafa majalisa na cikin ajandar sa, kuma idan ya zama dole, zai ziyarci dukkan jihohin da zai iya, a lokacin da ake gab da fara yakin neman zabe".
Metro News ta West Virginia ta ruwaito cewa taron da aka shirya a daren yau a filin Wispango a Wheeling zai iya samun magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh za su rufe shi".
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Senate na Republican a West Virginia, wanda ke da karamin kuri'a.
A cewar Reuters, Simon Heider, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ya ce, "Sanin cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi nasara a kan Mauricio a zaben ba alama ce mai kyau a gare shi ba".
