HIV/AIDS: China ta ruwaito karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HIV da AIDS.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce sama da mutane 820,000 ne ke dauke da cutar a kasar.
A cikin watanni uku na biyu na 2018 kawai, an ba da rahoton sabbin shari'o'i kusan 40,000.
Mafi yawan sabbin cututtukan ana yada su ne ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan yana nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin saboda yaduwar cutar ta jini.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun bayyana a wani taro a lardin Girka cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da mutum 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta zama babban matsala a cikin al'ummar Sin.
An yi la'akari da yin luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana zargin cewa nuna bambanci ga masu jinsi daban-daban yana da yawa.
Saboda dabi'un da kasar ke da shi na ra'ayin mazan jiya, binciken da aka gudanar ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na mazajen da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata a ƙarshe.
Yawancin cututtukan da ke yaduwa suna haifar da rashin kulawa ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin China ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV a duk duniya a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
