A ranar Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara wanda ke da babban jerin taurari da ke yin wasan kwaikwayon kuma yana da manufa mai ban mamaki: kawo ƙarshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Citizen's World zai ga dubun dubatar mutane suna gangarowa zuwa babban ciyawa na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci zuwa 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka sanar a shekarar 2012, ya kasance wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don wannan taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar za su yi jerin ayyuka, ko "aiki" kamar ba da kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kowane irin hanyar da ta dace don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawo karshen talauci.
