Wannan furucin ya zo ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump, ta maye gurbin Rasha, ke aiki kan manufarta ta kara fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai da kuma samar da hanyoyin da suka fi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
A wannan yanayin, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin karfafawa Jamus gwiwa ta janye daga aikin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda a cewar Trump, ya sa Berlin ta zama 'yar gudun hijira ga Rasha.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 mai dala biliyan 11, wanda zai kawo karfin bututun na yanzu zuwa murabba'in mita biliyan 110, zai zama cikakken shiri mai tattalin arziki.
Kremlin ya jaddada cewa halin da Washington ke ciki game da wannan aikin ya kasance ne kawai saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, wanda ya nuna cewa wannan misali ne na rashin lafiya.
Ministan makamashin Rasha Alexander Novak ya ce bayan ganawarsa da Ministan makamashin Amurka Rick Perry a watan Satumba a Moscow, "Na yi imanin cewa muna da ra'ayi daya cewa iskar gas ba za ta iya zama hanyar turawa ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zabar mai samar da iskar gas da kansu".
Batun Amurka ya haifar da mummunan martani daga Jamus, wacce ta sake tabbatar da jajircewarta ga aikin.
Babban cibiyar samar da masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industry (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guji manufofin makamashi na Turai da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), ya ce: "Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a samar da makamashinmu", bayan ganawar da aka yi tsakanin Angela Merkel, Firayim Ministan Jamus da Vladimir Putin.
Sanata daga Massachusetts Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi tunani sosai kan tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a zaben 2020.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi tunani sosai kan tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben na tsaka-tsakin.
A yayin wani taro a gidan shakatawa na gari a Holyoke, Sanata Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da tsayawa takara.
A cewar Hill, ta ce, "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su sake gina gwamnatin da ta lalace, kuma hakan zai yiwu ne kawai idan shugabanci na mata ne".
"Zan yi tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa, bayan 6 ga Nuwamba".
A lokacin da yake matsawa Shugaba Donald Trump, ya ce "wannan kasa tana kan hanyar da ba ta dace ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump zai yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji shi.
Warren ya bayyana kansa a cikin sukar da ya yi wa Donald Trump da Britt Kavanaugh, wanda ya tsaya takararsa a kotun koli.
A cikin wata tweet a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce, "Tabbas muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'a".
Binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis, duk da haka, ya nuna cewa mafi yawan masu jefa kuri'a ba su yi tunanin cewa ya kamata ya tsaya takara a zaben 2020 ba.
A cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston ta gudanar, kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce "watakila" bai kamata a zabi sanata ba.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan wannan rabon.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga Diwel Patrick, tsohon gwamna, tare da sauran kashi 38 cikin dari na goyon bayan yiwuwar shiga, kuma kashi 48 cikin dari sun nuna adawa.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna dangane da takarar zaben 2020 sun hada da Joe Biden, tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa da kuma Sanata Bernie Sanders, na Vermont.
Asoshin na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a watan Janairu.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da PTSD a lokacin da Donald Trump ya yi tafiya
Turk Palin, mai shekaru 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki kafin ya yi rajista a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a ranar Litinin da daddare, a cikin wani abin da ya faru na tashin hankali na cikin gida.
"Duk da abin da ya faru da ɗana, abin da ya faru da shi lokacin da ya dawo, na fahimci iyalan da ke fama da cutar PTSD da kuma raunin da sojojinmu ke fama da shi", in ji ta a jawabin da ta yi ga masu sauraro a bikin Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Paulin ya kira kama shi "giwa a cikin dakin", yana mai cewa dansa da sauran mayakan "sun dawo da bambanci amma sun fi karfi, sun dawo da jin cewa abin da sojoji da rundunar sojin sama da kowane memba na sojoji suka ba wa wannan kasar yana da daraja".
A cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun sashen 'yan sandan Walesa, an kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata a cikin gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida, da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye.
Jihohi 18 da D.C. sun goyi bayan kalubalen da aka yi wa sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan kalubalen shari'a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka na kin ba da mafaka ga wadanda suka kamu da aikata laifi ko tashin hankali na cikin gida.
NBC News ta ruwaito cewa, wakilan jihohi da gundumomi 18 sun gabatar da takardar neman izini a gaban kotun Washington a ranar Juma'a, a goyon bayan manufofin da ke kalubalantar 'yan gudun hijira.
Sunan mai kara a cikin shari'ar Grace v. Sessions, wanda ke ikirarin cewa kungiyar American Civil Liberties Union ta yi tawaye a watan Agusta kan manufofin tarayya na gidajen alfarma, ba a bayyana ba.
Ya ce abokin tarayyarsa "da 'ya'yansa maza da suka kasance cikin kungiyar masu cin zarafin" sun yi masa fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun ki amincewa da bukatarsa ta mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihar da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana cewa El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala sune kasashen da suka fi samun mafaka a Amurka saboda suna fuskantar gungun mutane da kuma tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta sauya shawarar da Hukumar Daukaka Kara ta Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wacce ta baiwa baƙi marasa tushe da suka tsere daga tashin hankali na cikin gida damar neman mafaka.
Janar Carl Racine, Sarkin Ruwa na District of Columbia, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
A takaice dai, karar ta ce kotun "ta bukaci dukkan bukatar neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman yanayi da kuma gaskiyar da ake nema a yi hukunci, kuma irin wannan takunkumin ya saba wa wannan ka'ida".
Lauyoyi a cikin wannan taƙaitaccen bayanin sun jaddada cewa manufar hana baƙi shiga cikin tattalin arzikin Amurka ta cutar da su, suna ƙara cewa suna iya yin kasuwanci kuma "suna samar da kuɗin da ake buƙata".
A watan Yuni, taron janar Jeff ya umarci alƙalan 'yan gudun hijira da su hana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin gida da kuma cin zarafin 'yan bindiga.
A cikin sanarwar manufofinta na ranar 11 ga Yuni, Sessions ya bayyana cewa "wanda ya bar kasarsa saboda tsoron mutuwa, saboda tserensa, addininsa, asalinsa, ko kuma kasancewarsa cikin wata kungiya ta siyasa ko ta zamantakewa, zai iya samun mafaka".
Bautar ba ta taɓa rage dukkan matsaloli ba - har ma da manyan matsaloli - waɗanda mutane ke fuskanta a rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun.
An yi kokarin ceto a Palo, yayin da aka ninka adadin wadanda suka mutu a kokarin neman wadanda suka tsira.
Yanayin ya zama mummunan yanayi ga waɗanda suka tsira.
Risa Kasma, wata mahaifiyar mai shekaru 35 da ke kula da ɗanta mai zazzabi a daya daga cikin cibiyoyin fitar da mutane a garin Palo, ta ce "abin bakin ciki ne".
"A kowane lokaci, motar asibiti za ta kawo gawarwakin.
Ruwa mai tsafta yana da ƙarancin".
An ga mazaunan suna komawa gidajensu da suka lalace, suna jan kayansu daga ruwa, suna ƙoƙarin ceton abin da suka iya.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni kuma asibitoci sun cika da raunuka a girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Duo Harris, wanda ya karye kashin baya da kafada, sun kwanta a waje da asibitin soja na Palo, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya sakamakon girgizar kasa mai tsanani.
Idanunsa suka cika da hawaye yayin da yake tunanin yadda girgizar kasa ta girgiza dakin da yake zama a dakinsa na biyar da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Ba lokacin da za mu ceci ranmu ba.
Harris ya shaida wa Asoshin Jakadancin cewa, "Ina tsammanin na kasance a cikin rushewar ganuwar", ya kara da cewa, iyalinsa sun tafi gari don bikin aure.
"Na ji muryar matar tana kuka don taimako, amma sai na ji muryar kashewa.
Ba na san abin da ya faru da shi ba, kuma ba na san abin da ya faru da shi ba.
Ina fata sun kasance lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "yin dariya" ta hanyar "tallan talla".
Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna fa'idar cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba bayan da ya zargi China da sha'awar tsoma baki a zaben Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta, yana mai ambaton wata jaridar kasar Sin da ta biya kudin shiga ga jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, Des Moines Register.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na son shiga tsakani a zaben Amurka ya nuna wani abu da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne na kara fafutuka da Washington ke yi domin matsa wa China.
Duk da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su fitar da sanarwarsu don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci wanda ya ga karin haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
Masana harkokin kasuwanci na kasar Sin da na Amurka sun ce an tsara takunkumin da kasar Sin ta yi a farkon yakin ne domin a yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki hari a jihohin Chao Phraya, wanda jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump ke goyon bayanta.
Terry Bernstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan jihar Lau, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikata, manoma da kamfanonin Amurka.
"Sai China ta ninka wannan abin dariya ta hanyar gabatar da sanarwar farfaganda a cikin kafofin watsa labarai na 'yanci na kasarmu", Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani rahoto a cikin Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi.
"Ta hanyar dakatar da farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da kuma kafofin watsa labarai na 'yanci, ta hanyar buga sanarwa a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a cikin wani karamin rumfar labarai a nan Beijing, za ku ga 'yan muryoyin adawa kaɗan kuma ba za ku ga ainihin abin da ke nuna ra'ayoyi daban-daban da jama'ar Sin za su iya yi game da hanyar da tattalin arzikin ke shiga ba, ciki har da cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya yi kasa a gwiwa kan buga labarin", duk da haka, bai ambaci sunan jaridar ba.
Manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican za su iya raba mata masu jefa kuri'a da mummunan halin Kwanzaa kafin zaben tsakiyar lokaci
Yayin da 'yan Republican da dama ke kare matsayin Britt Kwanuwa, dan takarar shugaban kasa, kan zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su fuskanci mummunar amsa, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben da ke tafe.
Matsayin jin daɗi ya yi yawa, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican da ke cikin jerin sun nuna cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Grant Richer, Farfesa a Makarantar Shari'a ta Jami'ar Syracuse ta Maxwell, a cikin wata kasida da ta bayyana a ranar Asabar, ya ce, "Ba za a iya yin watsi da irin wannan batun ba".
Richter ya ce yana da shakku game da kokarin da Sanata Jeff Felix ya yi a lokacin karshe na tabbatar da cewa binciken FBI ya isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
A cewar jaridar Washington DC, Karin Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, "Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba".
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga yayin da suke ratsawa ta cikin zauren majalisar dattawa, sun yi ta ihu suna "Lambar ta zo!" saboda 'yan Republican suna da iko da kwamitin shari'a da suka zaba don ci gaba da takarar Kwankwato, duk da cewa, a cewar Mace, Dokta Christine Beasley Ford ta yi shaida.
"Democratic sha'awa za ta kasance a waje", in ji Steve Roddenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa na waje, ga shafin labarai.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya kai ga tsaunuka, gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin birane da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, 18-29 da ba sa son shugaban kasa, yawanci ba sa jefa kuri'a. "
Tun kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili game da cikakkun bayanai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar babban alkalin, manazarta sun ba da shawarar cewa idan 'yan Republican suka yi ƙoƙari su tabbatar da shi, za a iya samun rikici.
A cewar NBC News, Michelle Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee a farkon makon da ya gabata ya ce "ya haifar da babbar damuwa ga GOP".
Guy Sencil, shugaban Amurka Priorities, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ya shaida wa CNN cewa "ba wai kawai batun kwamitin zabe ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe kan ko Kavanaugh zai fito a kan kujerar zabe, amma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka dauki mataki da kuma yadda suka bi da shi".
Koyaya, Amurkawa suna da alama sun yarda da wani ɓangare na Ford da shaidarsa a kan Kavanaugh, tare da ɗan gajeren ga Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford ko kuma sun yi imani da shi, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh ko kuma sun yi imani da shi.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin 100 na Fed sun ce suna tunanin ko Kovana ko alƙali na iya yin ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce daidai da Ford.
Bayan kokarin Flake, FBI ta fara binciken ta kan zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma akalla wani mai tuhuma, Deborah Ramirez.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya rantse a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa fyade a lokacin da yake cikin maye, lokacin da yake dan shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna masa na'urar haifuwa yayin da suke cikin wani taro a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale, a 1980.
Gano mai binciken yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin samar da sabon intanet don ya yi wasa da Google da Facebook
Kungiyar Birner-Lee, mai binciken Intanet ta duniya, ta fara takawa Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon aikin fasaha mai ban mamaki shine Inrupt, kamfanin da ke gina dandamali na tushen tushen SolidBrain.
Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda aka ba izinin samun damar wannan bayanin.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Birners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa burinsa bayan Inrupt shine "yin mulki a duniya".
Ya ce game da matakan farko, "Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu".
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan kayan aikin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "shafin yanar gizon kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Shagon yana da jerin abubuwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kayan ado, kiɗa, ɗakin karatu da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Wannan yana samuwa a cikin Drive Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Silk da Spotify duk a cikin wani mai bincike a lokaci guda.
Abinda ke da mahimmanci game da shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri shine cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Ka'idar Inrupt, a cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya hada albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu yana da Birners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ke bayarwa, da kuma wasu ma'aikatan kwangila da aka tura don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma kwamitin masu ba da gudummawa.
Farawa a wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar kayan aikin su na rarraba, ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Birners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana game da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a yi canji na gaba daya, inda sauran tsarin kasuwanci suka zama cikakke a cikin ƙwanƙwasa ido".
"Ba mu neman izini ba".
A cikin wani sakon da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar, Birners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa cikin daidaito da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizon da aka kirkira a Solid.
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya kafa Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Consortium na Yanar gizo a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin tattaunawar da ba ta da ma'ana.
Ko da lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance a matsayin wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
