Mickelson, wanda ke buga gasar a karo na 12, ya sami damar zama a kan kujera daga kyaftin Jim Forick don kwallaye hudu da ya yi a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama cibiyar aiki, kamar yadda ya saba yi wa Amurka, wanda ya ci gasar cin kofin duniya biyar ya kwashe rabin kwanakinsa yana mai ba da tallafi da sauran rabin kwanakinsa yana aiki a kan wasan da yake fatan zai taimaka masa.
Wanda bai taɓa zama mai tseren mota ba, har ma a lokacin da yake kan gaba, mai shekaru 48 bai taɓa zama kyakkyawan zaɓi ba don tseren Golf na National League, inda dogon lokaci mai wahala ke haifar da mummunan sakamako kowace rana.
Kuma ba shakka ba hanya ce mai ban tsoro ba, Mickelson ya ci karo da gasarsa ta tara a ranar Lahadi, inda ya yi karo da gwarzon dan wasan British Open, Francisco Molinari, wanda ya hada hannu da Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa suka fara gasar ne da maki hudu a raga 12 kawai, kuma suka fara da zafi, za a iya tabbatar da cewa gasar Mickelson ta gaggawa ce.
