An sake jinkirta jirgin yakin Jamus
Kafofin yada labarai na gida sun ruwaito cewa sabon sansanin sojin ruwan Jamus ya kamata ya fara aiki a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin jirgin yakin Cold War, amma ba za a fara aiki ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda matsaloli a tsarin da kuma amfani da bindigogi.
A cewar jaridar Day Zet, kamar yadda mai magana da yawun Sojoji ya ruwaito, an dage fara aiki da Rhineland-Pittsfalz, babban jirgin ruwan Baden-Württemberg na zamani zuwa rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan canjin sun haifar da sauya makomar wannan babban aikin.
An umarci jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg-class daga rundunar sojan ruwa a 2007 don maye gurbin tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen-class.
An san cewa za su nuna manyan bindigogi, makamai masu linzami na jirgin sama da na jirgin ruwa, da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar radar, infrared da kuma rage siginar sauti.
Sauran mahimman abubuwan da suka dace sun haɗa da dogon lokaci na kiyayewa - wannan ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa daga tashar jiragen ruwa na cikin gida, don ayyukan shekaru biyu.
Dai Zeit ya nuna cewa, duk da haka, ana iya cewa jinkiri na dindindin yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu linzami waɗanda zasu ba Jamus damar tsara ayyukanta na waje za su ƙare da fara aiki.
Jirgin ruwan F125 wanda bai yi nasara ba ya kasance cikin jerin sunayen da suka gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta hana shi aiki kuma ta ba da shi ga kamfanin sayar da jiragen ruwa na Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta mayar da jirgin zuwa ga mai ginin jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san cikakken dalilin da ya sa aka janye jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi nuni da wasu "ɓangarorin software da na'ura" waɗanda suka sa ba zai yi amfani ba idan aka tura shi don aikin yaƙi.
Rashin ingancin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci musamman saboda jiragen Baden-Württemberg-class zasu jagoranci ƙungiyar sojoji 120 - kawai rabin ma'aikatan da suka yi aiki a cikin jirgin ruwan Bremen na baya.
Har ila yau, gaskiyar cewa jirgin ya fi nauyi ya zama abin ƙyama, yana rage aikin da kuma iyakance ikon sojojin ruwa don ƙara haɓaka na gaba.
Jirgin Rhineland-Palatinate mai nauyin tan 7,000 yana tafiya a cikin jirgin ruwa, wanda ya ninka nauyin jirgin da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga rashin ingancin kayan aiki, farashin duk aikin - gami da horar da ma'aikata - shima yana da matsala.
An ce farashin zai kai €3.1bn ($3.6bn) - €2.2bn fiye da yadda aka zata.
Matsaloli a cikin sabon jirgin ruwa na zamani suna da mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken barazanar kwanan nan na rage ƙarfin sojojin ruwa na Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus "tana fuskantar karancin jiragen ruwa da za su iya zuwa aikin".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta kara girma ne a tsawon lokaci, yayin da tsoffin jiragen suka daina aiki amma ba a sake gina su ba.
Ya bayyana cewa babu wani jirgin ruwan yaki na Baden-Württemberg da ya cancanci shiga rundunar sojin ruwa.
