Kakannin yau sune Shugabannin Sunderland Ishmael Nick Adokat, David Moyes, Sam Alvarez, Martin O'Neill, Rui Cayani, Gus Puyt da Paulo de Cano.
Tsohon shugaban kungiyar Atlantic ya ce ba ya jin tsoron bin wadannan sunaye a babban kulob din, yayin da ya ki amincewa da shawarwarin Barnsley da Ipswich Town.
"Abin da ya fi dacewa a gare ni a wannan lokacin shi ne, 'Zan iya sake komawa wannan kulob din a gasar Premier?'
"Domin tsarin da kuma abubuwan more rayuwa a kulob din, babu shakka zai kasance a cikin gasar Premier", in ji shi.
"Ba abu mai sauƙi ba ne don zuwa can, amma zan iya ganin kaina a nan kawai idan na sake dawo da kulob din".
Ross ya shafe shekaru uku yana aiki a cikin wannan sana'ar bayan ya yi aiki a matsayin mataimakin shugaban a Dembarton kuma ya yi aiki na watanni 15 a horar da Gary Hertz.
Daga nan sai ya taimaka wa Elva ta guji faɗuwa zuwa jere na uku, kuma a kakar wasa mai zuwa, ya jagoranci St. Marine daga faɗuwa zuwa lashe gasar.
Kuma Ross ya ce yanzu yana jin dadi fiye da yadda ya yi a lokacin da yake wasa a Slade, Hartlepool, Fall Creek, St. Marine da Hamilton Academical.
Ya tuna lokacin da yake kula da al'ummar al'ummar, "Wannan wataƙila ya kasance ainihin al'umma".
"Na yi imani da gaske cewa aiki ya fi dacewa da ni fiye da wasa.
Abin mamaki ne saboda na yi aiki mai kyau, saboda haka na yi rayuwa mai kyau kuma na ji daɗin wasu manyan mukamai.
Amma wasa zai iya zama da wuya.
Akwai abubuwa da yawa da za ku sha wahala kowane mako.
